headline: IonQ, On Holding, Bloom Energy & Conagra: Market Minute
summary: Here are some of the stocks on the move on April 1, 2025. Shares of IonQ (IONQ) are rising after announcing its flagship quantum computer will be available to customers globally. On Holding (ONON) announced it is moving to a single CEO model, with co-CEO Marc Maurer to leave the company. Bloom Energy (BE) is teaming up with Conagra Brands (CAG) on fuel cell technology. Stay up to date on the latest market action, minute-by-minute, with Yahoo Finance's Market Minute.

headline: Conagra Brands Collaborates with Bloom Energy to Utilize Fuel Cell Technology at its Ohio Production Facilities
summary: Conagra Brands, Inc.
